{"id":238745,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-北京石榴庄村民孙双燕派出所内喝农药自/","date":"2012-07-09T10:46:16Z","modified":"2012-07-09T10:46:16Z","title":"维权网 | 北京石榴庄村民孙双燕派出所内喝农药自杀（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-E-tUEIYqPOI/T_qRLLBAwFI/AAAAAAAAJHo/-UDI7R8vDKI/s1600/1.jpg\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><img border=\"0\" height=\"201\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-E-tUEIYqPOI/T_qRLLBAwFI/AAAAAAAAJHo/-UDI7R8vDKI/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>石榴庄村被强拆现场</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2cyHQLXprZo/T_qRcZH9OmI/AAAAAAAAJHw/ePg9_YM3DUQ/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"204\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2cyHQLXprZo/T_qRcZH9OmI/AAAAAAAAJHw/ePg9_YM3DUQ/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7月6日到天安门附近散步的石榴庄村民</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成、孙雨报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，北京丰台区南苑乡石榴庄村多位村民因房屋遭强拆到天安门散步，被警察扣押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，村民孙双燕（图左一）在南苑派出所绝望之下喝农药自杀，以死抗争生存权被剥夺。被送往</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">307</span><span>医院抢救后暂无生命危险，目前留医院观察。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点多钟，有组织，统一着装拿着长短棍和盾牌的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span>多人冲进北京市丰台区石榴庄村，砸开村民的防盗门，采取断电，断网，砸毁摄像头等手段，周杰</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>多岁的老母亲被打伤拖走，家中几十万的财产丢失，多位村民也遭到同样的抢劫和强拆。周杰报警几十次警察始终没有露面，整个强拆过程中有多位村民被打伤。</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，房屋同样遭遇强拆的村民周杰接受采访时曝光本村遭遇。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>早上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>点，周杰家再次遭到报复性强拆，以前被拆得剩一半的家彻底消失变成一片废墟，侥幸剩下的家具也全部被埋废墟之下。村委会还扬言要给周杰定个叛国罪。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/07/blog-post_4272.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/07/blog-post_4272.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-3651213874229403541?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/dc259f202.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}